- Side…

337
00:20:06,854 --> 00:20:07,729
- That was hard, bro.
- Thank you.

338
00:20:07,812 --> 00:20:09,354
- See you on the field.
- That was cool.

339
00:20:09,437 --> 00:20:10,437
Thank you.

340
00:20:10,562 --> 00:20:13,021
