- Who?

344
00:20:18,271 --> 00:20:19,146
Ms. Vanity.

345
00:20:19,229 --> 00:20:20,187
…for Hip-Hop.

346
00:20:20,312 --> 00:20:21,479
Let's go.
She'll be in the crowd.

347
00:20:31,354 --> 00:20:33,771
It's an old story
From the alleys of Bombay

348
00:20:33,854 --> 00:20:36,229
The message of terror
Suhani in the locality

349
00:20:36,312 --> 00:20:38,687
At such a tender age
There is so much tension

350
00:20:38,771 --> 00:20:41,146
My father is a drunkard
Who splurges my mother's pension

351
00:20:41,312 --> 00:20:43,771
Jaggu also says, boss, agree

352
00:20:43,854 --> 00:20:46,187
Jai Veeru from Kurla consume cannabis

353
00:20:46,312 --> 00:20:48,771
A road of black and yellow taxis and autos

354
00:20:48,854 --> 00:20:51,312
From Andheri to Churchgate
Breakfast on the train

355
00:20:51,646 --> 00:20:53,687
This is Bombay

356
00:20:53,812 --> 00:20:55,729
No, bro. It's Mumbai

357
00:20:56,604 --> 00:20:58,687
This is Bombay

358
00:20:58,771 --> 00:21:00,687
No, bro. No, bro

359
00:21:01,521 --> 00:21:02,521
Move, move, move.

360
