Have you lost it?

443
00:24:47,521 --> 00:24:48,604
Stop the car.

444
00:24:48,687 --> 00:24:50,021
I'm not stopping this car.

445
00:24:50,104 --> 00:24:51,604
Stop the car!

446
00:24:51,687 --> 00:24:53,229
