519
00:28:22,854 --> 00:28:23,771
Like you.

520
00:28:36,312 --> 00:28:39,604
Serious snack attack, you gave
Ms. Vanity.

521
00:28:39,687 --> 00:28:41,979
You've got her feeling the aura,

522
00:28:42,104 --> 00:28:45,521
my bro is Aala Flowpara!

523
00:28:56,354 --> 00:28:57,271
Babe…

524
00:28:57,937 --> 00:29:00,604
