and you got impressed?

525
00:29:01,979 --> 00:29:03,229
Not exactly.

526
00:29:03,687 --> 00:29:06,687
But yeah, he's kind of interesting.

527
00:29:09,271 --> 00:29:10,521
Interesting.

528
00:29:13,021 --> 00:29:13,979
What next?

529
00:29:14,104 --> 00:29:15,104
Spill.

530
00:29:15,437 --> 00:29:16,562
Come on.

531
00:29:17,812 --> 00:29:20,479
Bro, she isn’t going to text.

532
00:29:20,604 --> 00:29:22,729
