1101
01:09:26,687 --> 01:09:27,562
Vasanta!

1102
01:09:53,771 --> 01:09:55,104
Hello, madam!

1103
01:09:59,146 --> 01:10:00,062
Madam!

1104
01:10:09,312 --> 01:10:10,229
Hello, madam!

1105
01:10:12,271 --> 01:10:13,229
Hello!

1106
01:10:15,146 --> 01:10:16,479
Your noodles, ma'am.

1107
01:10:16,979 --> 01:10:17,896
Rise and shine.

1108
01:10:29,354 --> 01:10:30,646
Hope she's not dead.

1109
01:10:32,729 --> 01:10:33,604
Anyone there?

1110
