Yes, don't stress.

1122
01:11:11,479 --> 01:11:12,396
Okay, fine.

1123
01:11:12,521 --> 01:11:14,312
I'm calling it a day, okay?

1124
01:11:15,021 --> 01:11:15,896
Yes.

1125
01:11:46,312 --> 01:11:49,479
Eyes of a vulture
The lions are roaming fearlessly

1126
01:11:49,562 --> 01:11:51,062
Dreams of those with open eyes

1127
01:11:53,187 --> 01:11:54,687
Help!

1128
01:12:32,646 --> 01:12:33,812
Hasn't it been fixed yet?

1129
