- No thanks, sir.

1139
01:12:58,604 --> 01:12:59,521
Take it.
Chow down.

1140
01:13:00,187 --> 01:13:01,062
Don't be formal.

1141
01:13:03,104 --> 01:13:04,521
Honestly, I was starving.

1142
01:13:05,562 --> 01:13:06,479
- Sir.
- Yes?

1143
01:13:06,854 --> 01:13:07,937
Can I take a selfie?

1144
01:13:08,521 --> 01:13:09,687
- With me?
- Yes, sir.

1145
01:13:09,771 --> 01:13:11,229
I'll have some major cred
with the boys in

1146
01:13:11,312 --> 01:13:12,562
my hood when they see
I'm pals with a top cop.

1147
01:13:13,271 --> 01:13:14,146
Click, fast.

1148
01:13:16,104 --> 01:13:18,062
