coconuts and killed it.

1153
01:13:24,396 --> 01:13:25,604
- Really?
- Yeah.

1154
01:13:25,937 --> 01:13:29,146
See, we wrecked the forests,

1155
01:13:29,521 --> 01:13:30,521
