1156
01:13:31,354 --> 01:13:32,812
Filled lakes to build towers.

1157
01:13:33,646 --> 01:13:35,437
- Where are the crocodiles supposed to go?
- Right.

1158
01:13:37,146 --> 01:13:38,687
- I'm off. Duty first.
- Okay, sir.

1159
01:13:38,854 --> 01:13:40,104
- Catch you later.
- Thanks for everything.

1160
01:13:40,771 --> 01:13:41,646
Bye.

1161
01:13:41,729 --> 01:13:42,646
- Sir.
- Yes?

1162
01:13:43,062 --> 01:13:44,562
- Seatbelt.
- Oh.

1163
01:13:44,812 --> 01:13:46,312
See, I noticed.

1164
01:13:50,354 --> 01:13:52,479
Hope it doesn't act up again.

1165
01:14:24,896 --> 01:14:25,812
Popo!

1166
01:14:37,812 --> 01:14:39,146
Is anyone there?

1167
01:14:48,604 --> 01:14:50,187
Help!

1168
01:15:20,687 --> 01:15:21,729
Flow!

1169
01:15:25,729 --> 01:15:27,021
Is anyone there?

1170
01:15:29,229 --> 01:15:30,604
Help!

1171
01:15:34,104 --> 01:15:35,854
Flow!

1172
01:15:37,396 --> 01:15:39,854
Help!

1173
01:17:33,604 --> 01:17:34,771
Call Flow!

1174
01:17:43,479 --> 01:17:44,479
Call Flow!

1175
01:17:56,771 --> 01:17:57,729
Come on, pick up.

1176
01:17:57,937 --> 01:17:59,354
Pick up.

1177
