1187
01:19:21,896 --> 01:19:22,812
Vasanta!

1188
01:19:36,812 --> 01:19:37,729
Avani!

1189
01:19:44,312 --> 01:19:45,729
Come on!

1190
01:19:50,187 --> 01:19:51,521
Come on!

1191
01:19:54,271 --> 01:19:55,146
Avani!

1192
