1194
01:20:04,812 --> 01:20:05,729
Avani!

1195
01:20:06,729 --> 01:20:08,271
Get up, Avani, please.
Avani!

1196
01:20:10,854 --> 01:20:11,771
Hello!

1197
01:20:13,771 --> 01:20:14,687
Avani!

1198
01:20:15,021 --> 01:20:15,896
Avani!

1199
01:20:18,062 --> 01:20:18,937
Avani!

1200
