I don't know.

1204
01:20:47,604 --> 01:20:48,937
How did you fall?

1205
01:20:50,937 --> 01:20:52,062
Did Vasanta do something?

1206
01:20:53,979 --> 01:20:54,854
I don't know.

1207
01:20:57,187 --> 01:20:59,187
Okay, wait.
I'll figure something out. Wait.

1208
01:21:03,229 --> 01:21:04,104
Flow!

1209
