Hello! Hello--

1238
01:23:04,896 --> 01:23:05,812
Fabric?

1239
01:23:06,479 --> 01:23:07,604
You called Fabric?

1240
01:23:07,687 --> 01:23:08,604
Phone's dead.

1241
01:23:08,812 --> 01:23:10,896
- Should have called the cops instead!
- The phone is dead.

1242
01:23:13,521 --> 01:23:14,479
You better not say a word.

1243
01:23:14,687 --> 01:23:15,937
This is all your fault.

1244
01:23:17,396 --> 01:23:18,312
You're jinxed.

1245
01:23:22,854 --> 01:23:24,354
You think this is my fault?

1246
01:23:26,771 --> 01:23:28,271
You were told to stay away
from the pool.

1247
01:23:28,979 --> 01:23:30,312
But do you ever listen to anyone?

1248
01:23:31,729 --> 01:23:33,104
Keep swimming in your pool now.

1249
01:23:34,479 --> 01:23:36,021
How do you even unlock this phone?

1250
01:23:39,604 --> 01:23:40,646
Unbelievable!

1251
01:23:41,687 --> 01:23:43,812
You think I did this on purpose?

1252
01:23:43,896 --> 01:23:45,521
We're stuck here because of you.

1253
01:23:48,021 --> 01:23:50,021
If you hadn't been so stubborn,
we'd be halfway to Goa.

1254
01:23:54,979 --> 01:23:56,104
It's all my fault.

1255
01:23:56,604 --> 01:23:58,062
You didn't do anything, right?

1256
01:23:59,146 --> 01:24:00,062
No, I did.

1257
01:24:01,271 --> 01:24:02,771
I followed you here.

1258
01:24:04,021 --> 01:24:05,021
So go back.

1259
01:24:05,271 --> 01:24:07,396
- Go… just leave.
- Go where?

1260
01:24:08,479 --> 01:24:09,354
Where?

1261
01:24:10,437 --> 01:24:13,604
Some genius made this pool
20 feet deep with no ladders!

1262
01:24:17,021 --> 01:24:18,354
Damn it, I'm trapped in here now.

1263
01:24:22,104 --> 01:24:24,812
Help!

1264
01:24:25,854 --> 01:24:29,312
Somebody, help!

1265
01:24:30,604 --> 01:24:32,937
Help!

1266
01:24:33,687 --> 01:24:34,979
Help!

1267
01:24:36,479 --> 01:24:38,104
Somebody help!

1268
01:24:42,896 --> 01:24:44,437
Oh God, please save me as well.

1269
01:25:03,729 --> 01:25:04,604
Avani!

1270
01:25:04,937 --> 01:25:05,812
I unscrewed it.

1271
01:25:06,187 --> 01:25:07,062
Avani!

1272
01:25:34,479 --> 01:25:36,104
Come on, come on, come on!

1273
01:26:15,396 --> 01:26:16,354
Hello!

1274
01:26:17,562 --> 01:26:18,687
Is anyone there?

1275
01:26:21,312 --> 01:26:22,312
Hello!

1276
01:26:37,854 --> 01:26:38,979
Is anyone there?

1277
01:26:40,771 --> 01:26:41,812
Avani.

1278
01:26:43,062 --> 01:26:44,062
Help!

1279
01:26:44,479 --> 01:26:45,521
Avani!

1280
01:27:15,104 --> 01:27:16,812
Help!

1281
01:27:18,187 --> 01:27:19,229
- Who was it?
- Help.

1282
01:27:19,354 --> 01:27:20,312
Did someone come?

1283
01:27:20,771 --> 01:27:22,187
I heard a car.

1284
01:27:24,104 --> 01:27:26,104
- Help!
- Help!

1285
01:27:26,229 --> 01:27:27,771
Is anyone out there?

1286
01:27:28,729 --> 01:27:29,854
Help!

1287
01:27:29,937 --> 01:27:31,021
Help!

1288
01:27:31,104 --> 01:27:32,271
Help!

1289
01:27:35,187 --> 01:27:36,479
Help!

1290
01:27:42,646 --> 01:27:43,687
I think they are gone.

1291
01:27:47,104 --> 01:27:48,562
You should've screamed louder.

1292
01:27:49,896 --> 01:27:50,854
Had you screamed louder…

1293
01:27:55,771 --> 01:27:56,687
What else could I do?

1294
01:27:56,771 --> 01:27:58,521
Someone was here, but they left.

1295
01:27:58,604 --> 01:27:59,979
You blew our chance.

1296
01:28:00,687 --> 01:28:03,521
Avani, you just kept whistling…
And just shut him up!

1297
01:28:04,312 --> 01:28:05,479
Popo, quiet!

1298
01:28:07,229 --> 01:28:08,729
Did you see an exit through the drain?

1299
01:28:11,646 --> 01:28:13,312
Shut him up, or I will…

1300
